<h1 id="lab-test-driven-development-tdd-in-python">Lab: Test-Driven
Development (TDD) in Python</h1>
<h2 id="objective">Objective</h2>
<p>Learn the basics of TDD by writing tests before implementing
code.</p>
<hr />
<h2 id="steps">Steps</h2>
<h3 id="1-set-up-your-environment">1. Set Up Your Environment</h3>
<ul>
<li>Ensure Python and <code>pytest</code> are installed.</li>
<li>Create a new Python file, e.g., <code>calculator.py</code>.</li>
<li>Create a test file, e.g., <code>test_calculator.py</code>.</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="2-write-a-failing-test">2. Write a Failing Test</h3>
<p>In <code>test_calculator.py</code>:</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb1"><pre
class="sourceCode python"><code class="sourceCode python"><span id="cb1-1"><a href="#cb1-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="im">from</span> calculator <span class="im">import</span> add</span>
<span id="cb1-2"><a href="#cb1-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb1-3"><a href="#cb1-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="kw">def</span> test_add():</span>
<span id="cb1-4"><a href="#cb1-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>    <span class="cf">assert</span> add(<span class="dv">2</span>, <span class="dv">3</span>) <span class="op">==</span> <span class="dv">5</span></span></code></pre></div>
<h3 id="3-run-the-test">3. Run the Test</h3>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb2"><pre
class="sourceCode bash"><code class="sourceCode bash"><span id="cb2-1"><a href="#cb2-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="ex">pytest</span> test_calculator.py</span></code></pre></div>
<ul>
<li>The test will fail because <code>add</code> is not implemented.</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="4-implement-the-function">4. Implement the Function</h3>
<p>In <code>calculator.py</code>:</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb3"><pre
class="sourceCode python"><code class="sourceCode python"><span id="cb3-1"><a href="#cb3-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="kw">def</span> add(a, b):</span>
<span id="cb3-2"><a href="#cb3-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>    <span class="cf">return</span> a <span class="op">+</span> b</span></code></pre></div>
<h3 id="5-run-the-test-again">5. Run the Test Again</h3>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb4"><pre
class="sourceCode bash"><code class="sourceCode bash"><span id="cb4-1"><a href="#cb4-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="ex">pytest</span> test_calculator.py</span></code></pre></div>
<ul>
<li>The test should now pass.</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="6-refactor-optional">6. Refactor (Optional)</h3>
<ul>
<li>Improve code if needed.</li>
<li>Ensure tests still pass.</li>
</ul>
